A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 County Boards of Education – Members – Publication of Contact Information
3 FOR the purpose of requiring the county school system of each county in the State to
4 publish prominently on its website certain contact information for each member of
5 the county board of education; and generally relating to members of county boards
6 of education.
7 BY adding to
8 Article – Education
9 Section 3–106
10 Annotated Code of Maryland
11 (2022 Replacement Volume and 2024 Supplement)
12 SECTION 1. BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF MARYLAND,
13 That the Laws of Maryland read as follows:
14 Article – Education
15 3–106.
16 EACH COUNTY SCHOOL SYSTEM SHALL PUBLISH PROMINENTLY ON ITS
17 WEBSITE THE CONTACT INFORMATION FOR EACH MEMBER OF THE RESPECTIVE
18 COUNTY BOARD, AS FOLLOWS:
19 (1) FOR NONSTUDENT MEMBERS:
20 (I) AN E–MAIL ADDRESS;
21 (II) A MAILING ADDRESS; AND
